1
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:30,060
Anchovy, have you been well?

2
00:00:33,240 --> 00:00:37,720
You'll know who I am just by hearing my voice.

3
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:43,900
In just a few days, a day more important than the one I lost my energy will come...

4
00:00:43,900 --> 00:00:47,040
That day is the day I lost my eye.

5
00:00:49,900 --> 00:00:51,060
Once a year...

6
00:00:52,580 --> 00:00:54,920
I chew on a pollack head...

7
00:01:00,590 --> 00:01:04,390
The closer that day gets, the more I think of you...

8
00:01:26,757 --> 00:01:28,230
Didn't I tell you?

9
00:01:28,510 --> 00:01:30,830
Maybe he's happy because he knocked down Anchovy.

10
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:56,469
